snippet.textDisplay: Can we acknowledge how talented and amazing Seth is.  A awesome guy born in Long Island, completely devoid of mountain bike trails.  Then Florida, and then to Asheville where his channel became huge!  Now to berm peak, where there’s never a dull moment.  I want to acknowledge all the subscribers that are currently watching and Seth, one of the coolest guys out there who developed an awesome channel that we all dream about.  Seth, you are amazing and we all love you and would do anything for you!  P.S, thanks for signing my hat at the Sedona mountain bike festival! Stay safe at home, and keep doing the impossible!
